	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la">Salve plurimum, frater dilectissime in Christo Iesu, domino et servatore nostro.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la">Literas tuas una cum libello<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1"><persName ref="p495">Bullingers</persName> Brief vom 18. September 1545 <hi>(HBBW</hi> XV, <ref target="file12293">Nr. 2246</ref>) und die ihm beigelegte "Orthodoxa <placeName ref="l587">Tigurinae</placeName> ecclesiae confessio" von März 1545; s. <bibl>HBBW XV</bibl> 532,23f.</note> mihi acceptissimo <persName ref="p8427">Guilielmus</persName><note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2"><persName ref="p8427">Wilhelm Reublin</persName> (s. <bibl>HBBW XV</bibl> 458, Anm. 16), der auch den vorliegenden Brief übermittelte; s. unten Z. 7f.</note> <placeName ref="l581">Znaymę</placeName><note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3"><placeName ref="l581">Znojmo</placeName>, <placeName ref="l921">Mähren</placeName> (<placeName ref="l3091">Tschechien</placeName>).</note> mihi obtulit.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la">Quę omnia quanto desyderio expectarim quantoque cum gaudio atque gloriatione etiam exceperim et exosculatus fuerim, non dicam, ne quid adulari videar.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" ana="salute">Atque hęc tantum nunc scribere licuit imprimisque oportuit, ne scriptis vestris, optimi fratres, ita videar offensus aut exacerbatus, ut per commodum etiam nuncium fraterne salutare vos posthac dedigner.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
			<div xml:id="div2" corresp="regest2">
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la">Cęterum, ut res meę se habeant, <persName ref="p8427">Guilielmus</persName> narrare poterit.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" ana="salute">Vale quam optime, mi <persName ref="p495">Bullingere</persName>, una cum symmystis omnibus totaque ecclesia, et domino Iesu per orationem me commendate.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
			<div xml:id="div3" corresp="regest3">
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la"><placeName ref="l513">Ulmę</placeName> <placeName ref="l2481">Svevorum</placeName>, 13. maii anno, etc., 46.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la">Raptim.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la"><persName ref="p8504">Leonhartus Soerinus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la">Si rescribere vacat, pergratum est; sed et fiat per hunc ipsum tabellarium.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la"><persName ref="p495">Heynrycho Bullingero</persName>, ecclesię <placeName ref="l587">Tigurinę</placeName> episcopo, fratri in Christo dilecto et colendo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
